  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 5 March 1925
---
He is the searcher of hearts. He transcends speech and reason. He knows
us and our hearts better than we do ourselves. He does not take us at
our word, for He knows that we often do not mean it, some knowingly and
others unknowingly.
